== 鏡座標準 ==
RMR的鏡座標準為兩個螺釘孔和兩個在角落的淺插口，充當緩衝鎖耳。<ref name="optics-info-footprints">{{Cite web |url=https://optics-info.com/footprints-on-red-dot-sights/ |title=Footprints/Mounting Standards on Red Dot Sights - Optics info |accessdate=2020-08-01 |archive-date=2019-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209023758/https://optics-info.com/footprints-on-red-dot-sights/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>該鏡座除了RMR以外，亦被Holosun瞄準鏡所採用。原廠為RMR生產的鏡架為：
* 低[[皮卡汀尼導軌|皮卡汀尼導軌]]鏡架
* 高皮卡汀尼導軌鏡架
* 低Weaver導軌鏡架
* ACOG附接鏡架
* 25.4毫米或30毫米狙擊鏡管附接鏡架

